In this example, the primary color is set to Colors.indigo, which is a cool and deep blue shade. The accent color is set to Colors.teal, which is a complementary cool color. The scaffold background color is set to Colors.grey[100], which is a light and neutral shade of grey. The app bar color is set to Colors.white, providing a clean and coordinated look.

The text styles and button colors are adjusted to match the color scheme accordingly.

Remember to update the MyApp widget to use this modified theme: